interesting points: The report is classified as confidential and part of Project Blue Book Special Report No. 14.
The report indicates that the submitted material consists of 3 negatives on one strip.
No visible photograph or image is contained within the film strip described in the report.
The report does not provide any details about the nature of the UFO sighting or other witness information.
The report indicates that the case number is 9255.
sighted object: no visible object, only a photographic negative strip
photographs: yes, 3 negatives on one strip, but no visible image
